# 🛡️ Awesome Hacking Tools & Resources (Ethical & Educational)

Collected by: Atik Mals  
Purpose: For learning cybersecurity, ethical hacking, red teaming, and OSINT.

---

## 📁 Reconnaissance Tools

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Amass** | Subdomain enumeration | https://github.com/owasp-amass/amass |
| **theHarvester** | Email, domain, and employee harvesting | https://github.com/laramies/theHarvester |
| **Shodan CLI** | Search internet-connected devices | https://github.com/achillean/shodan-python |
| **Recon-ng** | Full-featured web recon framework | https://github.com/lanmaster53/recon-ng |

---

## 🧪 Vulnerability Scanners

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Nmap** | Network scanner | https://github.com/nmap/nmap |
| **Nikto** | Web server scanner | https://github.com/sullo/nikto |
| **Nuclei** | Fast vulnerability scanner | https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei |
| **XSStrike** | Advanced XSS detection tool | https://github.com/s0md3v/XSStrike |

---

## 🛠️ Exploitation Tools

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Metasploit Framework** | Most used exploitation tool | https://github.com/rapid7/metasploit-framework |
| **SQLmap** | Automated SQL injection | https://github.com/sqlmapproject/sqlmap |
| **Commix** | Automated command injection | https://github.com/commixproject/commix |
| **BeEF** | Browser exploitation framework | https://github.com/beefproject/beef |

---

## 🎯 Privilege Escalation

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **WinPEAS / LinPEAS** | Windows/Linux privilege enum | https://github.com/carlospolop/PEASS-ng |
| **Watson** | Windows privilege escalation | https://github.com/rasta-mouse/Watson |
| **Linux Exploit Suggester** | Suggests Linux exploits | https://github.com/mzet-/linux-exploit-suggester |

---

## 🧰 Post-Exploitation Tools

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Empire** | PowerShell post-exploitation agent | https://github.com/BC-SECURITY/Empire |
| **Pupy** | Remote Access Tool in Python | https://github.com/n1nj4sec/pupy |
| **Sliver** | C2 framework by BishopFox | https://github.com/BishopFox/sliver |

---

## 👁️ Information Gathering (OSINT)

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Photon** | Web crawler for OSINT | https://github.com/s0md3v/Photon |
| **Sherlock** | Social media username checker | https://github.com/sherlock-project/sherlock |
| **Email2phonenumber** | Try to find number from email | https://github.com/martinvigo/email2phonenumber |
| **Maltego CE** | Visual OSINT tool | https://www.maltego.com/ (not GitHub) |

---

## 🔐 Wireless & Network Tools

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Aircrack-ng** | WiFi cracking | https://github.com/aircrack-ng/aircrack-ng |
| **Bettercap** | MITM framework | https://github.com/bettercap/bettercap |
| **Wireshark** | Packet analysis (GUI) | https://github.com/wireshark/wireshark |

---

## 🔓 Password Attacks

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Hashcat** | GPU password cracker | https://github.com/hashcat/hashcat |
| **JohnTheRipper** | Classic password cracker | https://github.com/openwall/john |
| **Hydra** | Network brute-force | https://github.com/vanhauser-thc/thc-hydra |

---

## 🎮 Game Hacking Tools (Educational)

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Cheat Engine** | Memory scanner & editor | https://github.com/cheat-engine/cheat-engine |
| **Aimbot Template** | C++ / Python sample bots | Search "aimbot memory hack" |
| **ReadWriteMemory** | Python library for memory editing | https://github.com/learn-more/python-ptrace |

---

## 📦 Payload Collections

| Name | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **PayloadsAllTheThings** | Big list of payloads | https://github.com/swisskyrepo/PayloadsAllTheThings |
| **FuzzySecurity** | Exploit development blog/tools | https://github.com/FuzzySecurity |
| **Red Team Attack Simulation** | Red team scripts | https://github.com/AlexisAhmed/Red-Teaming-Toolkit |

---

## 💬 Discord / Web Control

| Tool | Description | GitHub |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Discord RATs (educational only)** | Remote access via Discord | Search: `discord remote tool` |
| **Webhook-based Logger** | Python webhook loggers | Search: `discord webhook python logger` |

---

## 📚 Learning Platforms

| Platform | Link |
|----------|------|
| HackTheBox | https://hackthebox.com |
| TryHackMe | https://tryhackme.com |
| PortSwigger Web Academy | https://portswigger.net/web-security |
| OverTheWire | https://overthewire.org/wargames/ |
| CTFTime | https://ctftime.org |

---

> ⚠️ All tools are for **educational and ethical** hacking only.  
> Run inside **VirtualBox/Kali Linux** for safety.  
> Do **not use** against any system without **permission**.

